ConsList
Class ConsList

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--ConsList.ConsList
Direct Known Subclasses:
Cons, Nil
public abstract class ConsList
extends java.lang.Object

ConsList defines the data type of cons-lists: a Nil cons-list will be modelled by new Nil(); a Cons cons-list will be modelled by new Cons(h, t). We use the Composite Design Pattern to model cons-lists.
